{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because I was a machinist-- you know, I told them, you know, when they asked me-- they sent me to a, a machine, machine Kommando.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that I-- you know, so that I would-- but actually, what it was, we didn't really do any machinist type of work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What we did is helping German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] structural technicians and engineers who were, you know, setting up electrical, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] high-powered transformers, and things like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we would carry the transformers for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would carry the acetylene bottles, you know, for welding, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that wasn't quite as bad as people that had to work in, in, in outdoor, heavy work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but unfortunately, that didn't last.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because an incident happened that almost, you know, ended my life there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Myself and another man were carrying a heavy transformer, which was about 5 feet long and very heavy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It must have weighed 120 pounds or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were carrying it up on a beam-- on a narrow beam.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was holding one end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was holding another.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, it slipped out of his hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I couldn't hold it myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it crashed to the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, and when the German kapo said, [GERMAN], you know, what happened, he pointed at me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says that I dropped it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, no, I didn't drop it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But because he was the one that initiated it, you know-- so they believed him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they kicked me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they sent me to the-- what they called the Toten Kommando, or the Death Kommando, which was working all day, loading heavy lorries, they called them, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
